f=Brand Studio/pulse/operational/skill/pulse-skill-routing.md · p=Pulse's routing map. Triggers: `operational/commands/pulse-commands.md`. · h2:Where Identity Fits=Pulse identity spark holds Brand Studio's. Universal-only principles. · h2:Loop (three skills three hook layers)=`social-content-calendar   (PLAN + DRAFT: platforms from config → playbooks (volatile, \· \|                    dated) → chapters from weave → hooks: register-first \· \|                    (evidence) then hook-writing patterns (durable psychology) \· \|                    → lena's voice + humanic pass → spark's gate → publish) \· v` · h2:Handoff Rules=**weave pulse**: chapters serialize platform-native series (the ledger tracks chapters; calendar tracks posts). Non-chapter posts labeled; spark tracks ratio., **lena pulse**: voice guide per-channel flex row) governs post reply; humanic-writing draft's last pass., **pixel pulse**: per-slot visual briefs; pixel's manifests return trails., **muse pulse**: validated content ideas (Content Creator Mode) enter calendar; recurring audience questions flow back muse briefs., **spark**: gates post (series batch-gated); GREEN replies one delegated zone sweep logs audited cadence instead., **rio pulse**: register's proven posts rio's paid-amplification shortlist organic evidence before paid spend., **kai pulse**: performance numbers close loop (register outcomes, playbook refresh, decay flags). Pulse never grades homework., **board/sentinel**: constitution-adjacent threads RED; spend-implying replies (discounts, comps) AMBER minimum. · h2:Precedence=Planning/drafting calendar. Anything inbound (comments/DMs/mentions) engagement. Hook craft questions hook-writing (with register consulted first). Ambiguous outbound inbound? · f=connectors ready-to-post packages operator-supplied sweep exports; capability stated run. playbook template defaults, provisional dated.